creator: Richard Crashaw
description:
LibriVox recording of A Hymn of the Nativity, Sung by the Shepherds by Richard Crashaw.
Read in English by Adele de Pignerolles; Ann Boulais; David Lawrence; Esther ben Simonides; Ed Humpal; Eileen Tipping; fshort; Leonard Wilson
Librivox volunteers bring you seven readings of A Hymn of the Nativity, Sung by the Shepherds by Richard Crashaw. This was the fortnightly poem for December 7 - December 21, 2014. - Ann Boulais
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
